Require the Inventory Committee to conduct complete physical count of its road networks in order to ascertain the existence of the balance of the account Road Networks;
Require the Designated General Services Officer to prepare a Report on Local Road Network, including a Road Map, at the end of accounting period and maintain the Local Road Network Property Card for all roads and its components;
Direct the Inventory Committee to prepare and submit copy of the RPCPPE to the Auditor in prescribed format, not later than January 31 of each year. In the preparation of the report, the different column should be properly filled out to ensure that all items are properly identified and accounted for; and
