Ensure that consolidated RAAF resulted from the consolidation of all the AOs’ individual RAAFs;
Require the MT to ensure inclusion of checks in her individual RAAF and, accordingly, in the consolidated RAAF;
Immediately verify the unaccounted ORs by providing details as to when said ORs where issued to payors and remitted to the Liquidating Officer (LO)/MT; and
Ensure preparation and submission of these RAAFs in accordance with the cited regulations.

