instruct the heads of implementing offices to expedite the implementation of BUB projects in order to provide the expected benefits to the intended beneficiaries on time;
instruct the heads of implementing offices to act promptly on disapproved proposals or on documents with discrepancies in order to hasten the approval and download of funds;

